PI06: 10th month of PI, 6th of 2017. 
	Each file read to be published gets staged into the git folder, being commited at the end  		of each PI06 session. 

	Even if PI06 changes name, the original scheme must continue untill the entire PI gets 		commited.
	
	Beyond PI, there is the OC&d related content, wich can be joined togheter or not,
	depending on the procedures.
	
	Translation must be done.
	The original content can be uploaded before or after, but both must be uploaded. 
	The order of release mostly impacts the spreading of info, wich can be greater
	in english at world level.
